ient Near East">Near Eastern</a>:</b> <a href="/wiki/Canaanite_religion" title="Canaanite religion">Canaanite</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ancient_Egyptian_religion" title="Ancient Egyptian religion">Egyptian</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Assyro-Babylonian_religion" title="Assyro-Babylonian religion">Assyro-Babylonian</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <b>Asian:</b> <a href="/wiki/Historical_Vedic_religion" title="Historical Vedic religion">Vedic</a></div>
